  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a survey to help understand the influences related to the decision for Adolescent&#xD;
      Idiopathic Scoliosis treatment (observation vs. bracing vs. surgery). The investigator then&#xD;
      plans to create a decision aid to help families when making a decision about the treatment&#xD;
      choice being presented to them.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This survey is designed to help understand the factors that families consider to help make&#xD;
      treatment decisions related to Adolescent Idiopathic Scoliosis (AIS). The surveys will then&#xD;
      be used to help create a shared decision making tool to help families better understand the&#xD;
      treatment options and optimize clinical conversations surrounding AIS treatment.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
